room_title: Escape room "The Boy With a Bean" by Escape Room Wisconsin in Green Bay
review: We had a blast! We did the Naughty List room with our kids (10 and 5) and had so much fun. We escaped with 14 minutes to spare--woo hoo! Can't wait to try another one.

room_title: Escape room "The Boy With a Bean" by Escape Room Wisconsin in Green Bay
review: Had a great time doing the Naughty List with friends. Got stumped a couple times but had fun. Very professional staff. Highly recommended!!
